    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, preserved in showroom condition and curated for the most discerning collector. This specimen exhibits an uncompromising level of care, featuring a flawless aesthetic profile and a mechanical integrity that mirrors its original factory specifications. An unrivaled opportunity to acquire a motorcar of distinguished caliber and investment-grade quality.",
      "price": 48500.0,
